thread.title: Matthew Reeves
thread.title_full: Ace Rental Cars Australia & New Zealand reviewed by Matthew Reeves

author: Matthew Reeves
title: Matthew Reeves
text: The car collection was a dream,we were in and out in 10 mins,the car was better amd bigger than expected,recent model and clean and good to drive.I liked the honesty of the staff when checking the car for damage etc and were very helpful on both occasions supplying maps and directions and a cab for getting back into the city after the drop off at Auckland.The extra insurance was also simple to understand and good piece of mind. Just cannot recommend ACE highly enough.
